                     <interp inst="t17991030-30-off168" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17991030-30-cd169" type="crimeDate">27th of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17991030-30-off168 t17991030-30-cd169"></join>, twelve yards of black ribbon, value 3s. two pair of cotton mittens, value 5s. and a silk handkerchief, value 4s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17991030-30-victim300" type="victimName">
