               <p>(The case was opened by Mr. Alley.)</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17991030-30-person307">
                  WILLIAM-BURNHAM
                   SHAW
               <interp inst="t17991030-30-person307" type="surname" value="SHAW"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17991030-30-person307" type="given" value="WILLIAM-BURNHAM"></interp>
